      <body>Although, I am not completely sure about the default here. Rails applications *must* default to :utc, but somehow AR defaults to :local? So I see why people are confused, but I don't think we can change the values today. Change the Railtie to local will break existing Rails applications, and changing AR will break AR usage outside Rails.</body>
