applications &lt;em&gt;must&lt;/em&gt; default to :utc, but somehow AR defaults
to :local? So I see why people are confused, but I don't think we
can change the values today. Change the Railtie to local will break
existing Rails applications, and changing AR will break AR usage
outside Rails.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
